data.eligibility_criteria:
Inclusion Criteria:

1. Healthy subjects, male and female, aged between 18 and 65 years, inclusive;
2. Body mass index: 18.0～28.0 kg/m2, inclusive; weight ≥50 kg for males and ≥45kg for females at enrollment;
3. Subjects (including their partners) agree to take highly effective contraceptive measure
